entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: The Rebel ally organization, the A.C.L.O. has been investigated through assiting them with their recent missions.
entries.journal_entry_description: Dathnaeya Loessin wants to investigate the Rebel Alliance and its allies.  Her contact at the Rebel office in Dearic is Captain Vayde Quellium, a boisterous, fun loving bothan.  Captain Quellium has asked that several missions be completed at the Nightstrike Soldier Hegemony base.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Captain Vayde Quellium has asked for assistance in helping him untangle some precarious situations involving the Aggregate Civil Liberties Organization and the Nightstrike Soldier Hegemony.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Complete the assignments Trezya and Vayde have given.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Captain Quellium has indicated that the A.C.L.O. representative currently in his office, the Twi'lek woman, Trezya Nenei, may have an important mission in the N.S.H. base which would coincide with his supply run mission.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Trezya Nenei related the A.C.L.O. plans to ambush an N.S.H. medical supply shipment.  She asked that the N.S.H. Enforcers intending to guard the shipment when it arrives be taken out.  Twenty five of them should be enough.
entries.task05_comm_message_text: You have done amazing taking out all those guards.  All that is left is their sergeant.
entries.task05_journal_entry_title: A Call from Trezya is Incoming
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: The shipment guards have been taken out.  All that is left is the sergeant.
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Captain Quellium needs supplies confiscated by the N.S.H.  The shipment would go a long way in helping the Alliance efforts on Talus.
